      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "It was rumored around labor cir\nGiles today that the Washington\nWater Power company contem-\nplates reeinstating the men who\nwere recently discharged for join\ning the union. After several days\nin which to think the the matter\nover, and as result of the ex-\npressions of all classes Of people\ncondemning the action of the COM\npany, it is considered likely that\nthe men may be again employed by\nthe local monopoly."
    }
